      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some minor fluid seeps and a suspension that is beginning to show its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and a few small tears, but the cabin remains smoke-free. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets you from A to B, but it is priced to reflect its current cosmetic and mechanical state.",
